{"tid":1254404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於體驗到中國有幾封閉，有幾抹殺言論自由","createTime":"2019-06-24T06:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T06:57:11.000Z","uid":22244,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"32dfcbc2a241fc169703f88e577dba69bf8576b3","tid":1254404,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我特登申請個小紅書ac黎做個小實驗<br />\n結果大家有具共睹啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講少少野發下感想都唔撚得<br />\n各位巴打，我會唔會俾中共捉返去架，好撚驚呀我屌你老母"},{"pid":"37da5e0747399c4e4fe4e99e69f3be1c6bdde554","tid":1254404,"uid":30067,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"乜係小紅書"},{"pid":"99b2f0f10a0fb8780be13278d6cb14311a0d8c6e","tid":1254404,"uid":105166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37da5e0747399c4e4fe4e99e69f3be1c6bdde554","tid":1254404,"uid":30067,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"乜係小紅書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"The red book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5b01491514ef3f114458643444220674b40efc","tid":1254404,"uid":14489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37da5e0747399c4e4fe4e99e69f3be1c6bdde554","tid":1254404,"uid":30067,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"乜係小紅書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:19:10.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10faddad2987d07bdf42b880f3c8fae4909dee6","tid":1254404,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:19:43.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n個server會on99咁好慢 凌晨時份會好啲 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=87a33f57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=4b62ffdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=97ecb518\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=447a7f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=e1296ba1\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=b9e6f3a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=343e5280\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"e78ce41c88114d0f3436f6abcae02cb132adb938","tid":1254404,"uid":53306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b2f0f10a0fb8780be13278d6cb14311a0d8c6e","tid":1254404,"uid":105166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37da5e0747399c4e4fe4e99e69f3be1c6bdde554","tid":1254404,"uid":30067,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"乜係小紅書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"The red book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-